import styles from './styles/custom.module.scss'
import { Navbar } from 'react-bootstrap'

const customNavbar = () => {
    return (
        <Navbar bg="light">
            <Navbar.Brand className={ styles.textTitle }>LOGO</Navbar.Brand>
            <Navbar.Toggle />
            <Navbar.Collapse>
                <Navbar.Text className="p-2">
                    Inicio
                </Navbar.Text>
                <Navbar.Text>
                    Nosotros
                </Navbar.Text>
                <Navbar.Text>
                    Contactanos
                </Navbar.Text>
            </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Navbar>
    )
}

export default customNavbar
